let d_43c285f34dc4e0891623d7f4be22efd0 = "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n  <head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width initial-scale=1\">\n\n  <title>A Set Of Certain Musings</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A set of musings about coding, computers, and perhaps some other things...\n\">\n\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/main.css\">\n  <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"http://christopherbothwell.com/\">\n  <link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/atom+xml\" title=\"A Set Of Certain Musings\" href=\"http://christopherbothwell.com/feed.xml\" />\n</head>\n\n\n  <body>\n\n    <header class=\"site-header\">\n\n  <div class=\"wrapper\">\n\n    <a class=\"site-title\" href=\"/\">A Set Of Certain Musings</a>\n\n    <nav class=\"site-nav\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"menu-icon\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 18 15\">\n          <path fill=\"#424242\" d=\"M18,1.484c0,0.82-0.665,1.484-1.484,1.484H1.484C0.665,2.969,0,2.304,0,1.484l0,0C0,0.665,0.665,0,1.484,0 h15.031C17.335,0,18,0.665,18,1.484L18,1.484z\"/>\n          <path fill=\"#424242\" d=\"M18,7.516C18,8.335,17.335,9,16.516,9H1.484C0.665,9,0,8.335,0,7.516l0,0c0-0.82,0.665-1.484,1.484-1.484 h15.031C17.335,6.031,18,6.696,18,7.516L18,7.516z\"/>\n          <path fill=\"#424242\" d=\"M18,13.516C18,14.335,17.335,15,16.516,15H1.484C0.665,15,0,14.335,0,13.516l0,0 c0-0.82,0.665-1.484,1.484-1.484h15.031C17.335,12.031,18,12.696,18,13.516L18,13.516z\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n\n      <div class=\"trigger\">\n        \n          \n          <a class=\"page-link\" href=\"/about/\">About</a>\n          \n        \n          \n        \n          \n        \n          \n        \n      </div>\n    </nav>\n\n  </div>\n\n</header>\n\n\n    <div class=\"page-content\">\n      <div class=\"wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"home\">\n\n  <h1 class=\"page-heading\">Posts</h1>\n\n  <ul class=\"post-list\">\n    \n      <li>\n        <span class=\"post-meta\">Dec 8, 2014</span>\n\n        <h2>\n          <a class=\"post-link\" href=\"/ocaml/mirage/linode/2014/12/08/hello-linode.html\">Hello Linode</a>\n        </h2>\n        <p>It has been almost a week since my last post and I\226\128\153ve been working on getting this blog setup on a Xen virtual machine. Most folks seem to be setting up their mirage kernels on Amazon\226\128\153s EC2 instances or their private Xen cloud platforms. I thought it might be nice to try it out on a different public clould/Xen provider. </p>\n\n\n      </li>\n    \n      <li>\n        <span class=\"post-meta\">Dec 3, 2014</span>\n\n        <h2>\n          <a class=\"post-link\" href=\"/ocaml/mirage/2014/12/03/about-not-found.html\">About Not Found</a>\n        </h2>\n        <p>After getting the blog set up initially running in Jekyll things seemed to be moving along smoothly to pushing this thing up to one of the various cloud platforms which might support running a mirage unikernel. The next testing phase was to get this set up to run locally inside the Unix option on my workstation. </p>\n\n\n      </li>\n    \n      <li>\n        <span class=\"post-meta\">Dec 3, 2014</span>\n\n        <h2>\n          <a class=\"post-link\" href=\"/jekyll/ocaml/hello/2014/12/03/hello-world.html\">Hello World</a>\n        </h2>\n        <p>Hello. I see you\226\128\153ve managed to stumble upon my first post here. Honestly, I just wanted to get something out. <a href=\"http://github.com/jekyll/jekyll\">Jekyll</a> seems to be a sufficiently complex tool and, like most times I have my first experience. I suppose I expect most folks that due this sort of thing are domain experts, or at least think they are. Suffice to say, I am not. Mostly I just see some bit of new technology or new idea and seek to gorge myself on the documentation, try a few things out, and then just move on\226\128\166like a buffet. So in the interest of keeping this a correct introduction here is the proverbial hello world. </p>\n\n\n      </li>\n    \n  </ul>\n\n  <p class=\"rss-subscribe\">subscribe <a href=\"/feed.xml\">via RSS</a></p>\n\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"site-footer\">\n\n  <div class=\"wrapper\">\n\n    <h2 class=\"footer-heading\">A Set Of Certain Musings</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"footer-col-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col  foote"
